Compares active treatment from single arm trial to observational study: very favorable context for the active treatment regarless of actual effect. **Seems like they do an STC, but basically center the covariates from the IPD trial to the value from the nonIPD trial by subtracting the mean of the nonIPD, and computes a linear regression using these new covariates values: to check that it comes down to the same thing as STC.**
